## information_listing — No Cart

No purchase flow. Show a contact form, lead capture, or external link.

```tsx
// No addToCart call — this type is for enquiries / lead generation
const handleEnquire = () => {
  router.push(`/contact?listing=${listing.id}`)
  // OR open a modal with a contact form
  // OR link to listing.account details for direct contact
}

// Hide: Add to Cart, Buy Now, price display (or show as "Contact for pricing")
// Show: Enquire button, seller contact info, listing.description
```

---

## video_listing — No Cart

Content access flow — not a purchase. May require auth for premium content.

```tsx
// No addToCart call — this type is for video/media access
const handleWatch = () => {
  if (requiresAuth && !isAuthenticated) {
    router.push('/sign-in')
    return
  }
  // Navigate to video player page or open modal with listing.videos[0]
  router.push(`/watch/${listing.slug}`)
}

// Show: Play button, listing.videos[0] preview
// Hide: price, Add to Cart, shipping info
```

