## requests — Reverse Marketplace

Buyer posts a need. Sellers respond with offers. No addToCart — this creates a request.

```tsx
// "requests" is a reverse marketplace flow — buyers post what they need,
// sellers bid or respond. This does NOT use the cart system.
// Auth required — guests cannot post requests.

const handleSubmitRequest = () => {
  if (!isAuthenticated) {
    router.push('/sign-in')
    return
  }
  // Navigate to request submission form, passing any pre-fill from this listing
  router.push(`/requests/new?category=${listing.category_id[0]}`)
}

// Show: "Post a Request" button, category, description as inspiration
// Hide: Add to Cart, price add-to-cart flow entirely
```

